<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<!--
  com.mukul.assistant-daemon — the single-process Assistant daemon.

  Collapses the com.assistant.assistant-pulse LaunchAgent (a 5-min timer) into
  ONE process: `python -m assistant`, run via bin/assistant-daemon.py. The
  daemon owns the pulse loop, the daemon heartbeat, tool dispatch, AND (when
  Slack is configured) the CommsSubsystem — each in its own thread of one
  process. No StartInterval: the daemon does not tick, it runs; KeepAlive
  relaunches it if it ever exits.

  THIS PLIST IS NOT LOADED BY THE INSTALLER. The migration is additive — the
  existing pulse agent keeps running until you switch over by hand.

  ⚠ IMPORTANT — the single daemon's CommsSubsystem SUBSUMES the standalone
  com.assistant.assistant-comms daemon (both broadcast the actions-ledger and
  page on a stale heartbeat to the SAME Slack channel, with SEPARATE cursors and
  no shared lock). Running both means every ledger entry pings you twice and
  every stale-heartbeat pages you twice. So when activating this daemon you MUST
  also unload assistant-comms.

  To activate (hand off pulse + comms to the single daemon):
    launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.assistant.assistant-pulse.plist
    launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.assistant.assistant-comms.plist  2>/dev/null || true
    launchctl load   ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.mukul.assistant-daemon.plist

  To roll back (restore the split pulse + standalone comms):
    launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.mukul.assistant-daemon.plist
    launchctl load   ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.assistant.assistant-pulse.plist
    # and, if you were running comms standalone before:
    # launchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.assistant.assistant-comms.plist
-->
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>Label</key>
    <string>com.mukul.assistant-daemon</string>
    <key>ProgramArguments</key>
    <array>
        <string>__PYTHON__</string>
        <string>__REPO__/bin/assistant-daemon.py</string>
    </array>
    <key>KeepAlive</key>
    <true/>
    <key>RunAtLoad</key>
    <true/>
    <key>ThrottleInterval</key>
    <integer>10</integer>
    <key>StandardOutPath</key>
    <string>__HOME__/.assistant/logs/assistant-daemon.launchd.out</string>
    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
    <string>__HOME__/.assistant/logs/assistant-daemon.launchd.err</string>
    <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>
    <dict>
        <key>HOME</key>
        <string>__HOME__</string>
        <key>PATH</key>
        <string>__PATH__</string>
    </dict>
    <key>WorkingDirectory</key>
    <string>__HOME__</string>
</dict>
</plist>
